ith an increased structural order in nanoconfined water. Our work opens up an\navenue to making capillaries and cavities with sizes tunable to {\\aa}ngstr\\\"om\nprecision, and with permeation properties further controlled through a wide\nchoice of atomically flat materials available for channel walls.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Jun 2016 11:23:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Sep 2016 13:16:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-18"}
